author: vhardy
msg: import statements clean up, thanks to Vladimir Bossicard's contribution. Now only have explicit imports (removed a few * imports. Removed unused imports. Imports now sorted in alphabetical order. Also, converted the few windows files to UNIX style

author: deweese
msg: JPEG Registry entry now has 'magic number' entry for EXIF files as well as JFIF
(This normally wasn't noticed since the JDK entry would pick it up, but
the JPEG entry is generally a bit faster than the JDK entry).

author: deweese
msg: Significant performance improvement for patterns that are filtered or have
filters applied to them (take Batik70 for example).

author: deweese
msg: X & Y values in JSVGViewerFrame are now once again in the viewBox coordinate
system (as is the W/H when mouse is out of the window).

author: deweese
msg: The Thumbnail dialog now takes document viewbox transform into account
when setting it's rendering transform up.
